Putting Consistency back into Eventual Consistency

   Valter Balegas ^1, 2 Sérgio Duarte ^2, 1 Carla Ferreira ^2, 1 Rodrigo
   Rodrigues ^2, 1 Nuno Preguiça ^2, 1 Mahsa Najafzadeh ^3, 4 Marc Shapiro
   ^4, 3 (BUTTON) Détails
   1 CITI - CITI Centre of Innovation in Telecommunications and
